{"tid":1852893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"估計順德已爆武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-30T16:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T17:45:55.000Z","uid":122940,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"484c9180a1018c416dd719011014651fa07fe7d3","tid":1852893,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200130/XKSIFIYLDJNBXG3SVOERJFWGQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200130%2FXKSIFIYLDJNBXG3SVOERJFWGQE%2F&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=d521500d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200130%2FXKSIFIYLDJNBXG3SVOERJFWGQE%2F&h=7a7422aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200130/XKSIFIYLDJNBXG3SVOERJFWGQE/</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎（WARS）疫情不斷擴散。據悉香港今日（30日）新增2宗初步確診（高度懷疑／初步陽性）個案，其中1宗是瑪嘉烈醫院內科病房的男病人，並非醫護人員，但涉嫌隱瞞曾訪<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>廣東順德</strong></span>，在內科病房播毒7日，當被發現初步確診後，才和盤托出，令同房的醫護和病人承受染病風險。<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記順德係2003年沙士的源頭。"},{"pid":"2639ad484bf702298de3ef7eb2bdcf04c947d7a1","tid":1852893,"uid":135277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"中山一日6單"},{"pid":"db90196c338ef798b8d8db57dc7535659a57db4a","tid":1852893,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:18:54.000Z","msg":"大陸狗定 on9 廢老"},{"pid":"0acc4fe4b5a442182f2d6a0d5138e82dfc4cab77","tid":1852893,"uid":122940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2639ad484bf702298de3ef7eb2bdcf04c947d7a1","tid":1852893,"uid":135277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"中山一日6單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"最驚係另一種病毒"},{"pid":"b1d0e3c3968556fde34585ed367d05084fd57c07","tid":1852893,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:19:57.000Z","