"tid":1852893,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:35:09.000Z","msg":"廣東應該有好快追到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n       確診<br />\n湖北4903 <br />\n浙江428<br />\n廣東354<br />\n<br />\n截至1月30日12時，廣東全省累計報告新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎確診病例354例。 <span style=\"color: red;\">30日0-12時全省新增確診病例43例</span>，新增出院病例2例。新增確診病例中，廣州市15例、深圳市12例、珠海市8例、東莞市4例、中山市2例、湛江市2例。有1514名密切接觸者正在接受醫學觀察。<br />\n<br />\n累計報告確診病例中，廣州市94例、<span style=\"color: red;\">深圳市98例</span>、珠海市26例、汕頭市12例、佛山市25例、韶關市4例、河源市1例、梅州市5例、惠州市17例、汕尾市1例、東莞市11例、<span style=\"color: red;\">中山市18例</span>、江門市1例、陽江市10例、湛江市11例、茂名市3例、肇慶市5例、清遠市6例、揭陽市6例。男性176例，女性178例，年齡介於11月齡-85歲之間。<br />\n<br />\n目前，重症37例、危重症13例，無死亡病例，累計出院病例8例。<br />\n(來源:廣東省衛健委網站)"},{"pid":"942193b070703bf1362a3aeab002026a9af219f9","tid":1852893,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0acc4fe4b5a442182f2d6a0d5138e82dfc4cab77","tid":1852893,"uid":122940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2639ad484bf702298de3ef7eb2bdcf04c947d7a1","tid":1852893,"uid":135277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:15:24.000Z","msg":"中山一日6單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:19:13.000Z","msg":"最驚係另一種病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:37:43.000Z","msg":"兩溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a4f8338182ba4812d40024665d8fe119bd3d54","tid":1852893,"uid":247019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"佢個女好似街市做"},{"pid":"524b1a979dbd762ae6107f71246f32453d98eda0","tid":1852893,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e92d42bc820628f97a1a9698cf3d1848c37f656","tid":1852893,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"